STARWARS
Episode IV, A NEW HOPE It is a period of galactic war.

Rebel spaceships, striking from a hidden outpost, have won their first victory against the evil Galactic Empire.
During the battle, Rebel spies managed to steal classified plans to the Empire's ultimate weapon, the DEATH STAR,
an armored space station with enough power to destroy an entire world.

Pursued by the Empire's sinister agents, Princess Leia races home aboard her starship, custodian of the stolen plans that can save her people and restore peace to the galaxy...
